<div class="container mt-5">
      <div>
        <h1><%= @concert.name %></h1>
      </div>
  <div class="d-flex my-5">
    <div class="details-info me-2">

      <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
        <div class="date pe-4">
          <h2 class="month"><%= @concert.date.strftime("%B") %></h2>
          <h2 class="day"><%= @concert.date.day %></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="vertical-line ps-4"></div>
        <div class="city-info d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
          <h4 class="address"><%= @concert.address %></h4>
          <h3 class="card-list-city">Amsterdam</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center me-7 my-3">

        <button type="button" class="card-list-button button-purple text-decoration-none" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#buddyModal">
          Buddies
        </button>
        <%= link_to "Interested", concert_forums_path(@concert), class:"card-list-button button-purple text-decoration-none"%>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="details-img ms-5">
       <%= image_tag('index-banner-pic.jpg', class: 'img-fluid') %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="d-flex">
    <div class="about-img me-4">
       <%= image_tag('index-banner-pic.jpg', class: 'img-fluid')%>
    </div>
    <div class="about-info">
      <h2 class="mb-4">About</h2>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Adipisci vero odit soluta. Est molestiae itaque at. Quaerat quidem at tempora perspiciatis in. Itaque tempore dignissimos quam voluptates inventore mollitia at.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Adipisci vero odit soluta. Est molestiae itaque at. Quaerat quidem at tempora perspiciatis in. Itaque tempore dignissimos quam voluptates inventore mollitia at.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Adipisci vero odit soluta. Est molestiae itaque at. Quaerat quidem at tempora perspiciatis in. Itaque tempore dignissimos quam voluptates inventore mollitia at.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="buddyModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="buddyModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable modal-lg">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="buddyModalLabel">Modal title</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="grid">
          <% if !@favorites.empty? %>
          <% @favorites.each do |f| %>
            <% image_tag "user-pic.png", class: "avatar dropdown-toggle", id: "navbarDropdown", data: { bs_toggle: "dropdown" }, 'aria-haspopup': true, 'aria-expanded': false %>
            <%= f.user.first_name %>
            <ul class="list-inline social-icons" >
              <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-facebook" style="font-size: 20px;"></i></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-twitter" style="font-size: 20px;"></i></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-instagram" style="font-size: 20px;"></i></li>
            </ul>
          <% end %>
          <% else %>
            <%= 'Buddies not found' %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
